Khartoum &mdash; President of the Republic, Field Marshal Omer Al-Bashir, Monday left for Saudi Arabia to perform Ummrah. He was seen off at Khartoum Airport by the First Vice - President of the Republic and National Prime Minister, Lt. Gen. Bakri Hassan Salih.He was accompanied by the Foreign Minister, Prof. Ibrahim Ghandour, and the State Minister at the Presidency and Director of the President's Offices, Hatim Hassan Bakhit.